"'''Shifting Gears'''" was a short story by [[Jean Rabe]] slated to appear in [[Star Wars Adventure Journal 17|''Star Wars Adventure Journal'' 17]], but was cancelled. In the story, a [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebel]] mission led by a [[Human/Legends|Human]] and a [[Zarian]] goes awry on [[Vengler]]. In the meantime, [[C1-EZ8]], an [[Assassin droid/Legends|assassin droid]], infiltrates a Rebel spy network on [[Tatooine/Legends|Tatooine]].

